n_of_stocks=2
prediction_days=200

def total_revenue_until_today():
    total_revenue=0
    total_transaction=0
    for moneyy in range(n_of_stocks):
        total_revenue=total_revenue+(stock_objects[moneyy].my_money-200)
        total_transaction=total_transaction+stock_objects[moneyy].my_transaction_number
    
    return total_revenue
    
    
def money_in_the_stocks():
    for moneyy in range(n_of_stocks):
        if stock_objects[moneyy].my_money>=200:
            print(str(indeces[moneyy])+"=="+str(stock_objects[moneyy].my_money)+" ₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺₺")
        else:
            print(str(indeces[moneyy])+"=="+str(stock_objects[moneyy].my_money))
        print(str(stock_objects[moneyy].my_transaction_number))
            
    
def printrmse():
    for rms in range(n_of_stocks):
        print("%s==%.2f" % (indeces[rms],stock_objects[rms].rmse))

    
    
class Stocks:
    def __init__(self,stock_id,stock_index):
        self.id=stock_id
        self.indd=stock_index
        #self.data=yf.download(stock_index, start="2020-01-01", end=str(today.date()))
        self.data=yf.download(stock_index, start="2019-01-02", end="2020-02-02")
        self.stock_hist=np.array(self.data['Close'])
        self.train=self.stock_hist[:(total_days-prediction_days)]
        self.test=self.stock_hist[-prediction_days:]
        self.my_money=200
        self.my_transaction_number=0
        self.errors=[]
        self.rmse=0
        
    def my_arimamodel(self):
        self.arimamodel=ARIMA(self.train, order=(4,1,0))
        self.arimamodel_fit = self.arimamodel.fit(disp=0)
        self.arima_output = self.arimamodel_fit.forecast()
        self.arima_output=self.arima_output[0][0]
        
        return self.arima_output
    
    def my_holtmodel(self):
        
        self.holtmodel=Holt(np.asarray(self.train))
        self.holtmodel_fit = self.holtmodel.fit(smoothing_level=.2, smoothing_slope=.02)
        self.holt_output=self.holtmodel_fit.forecast(1)[0]
        
        return self.holt_output
    
    def my_exponentialmodel(self):
        
        self.exponentialmodel=ExponentialSmoothing(self.train)
        self.exponentialmodel_fit=self.exponentialmodel.fit(smoothing_level=.3)
        self.exponential_output=self.exponentialmodel_fit.predict()[0]
        
        return self.exponential_output
    
    
    
    def update_train_and_test(self):
        self.train=np.append(self.train,self.test[0])
        self.test=self.test[1:]
        
    def make_decision(self):
        last_value=0.1*self.train[-1]+0.3*self.my_arimamodel() + 0.3*self.my_holtmodel() +0.3*self.my_exponentialmodel()
        self.errors.append(last_value-self.test[0])
        predicted_revenue=(last_value-self.train[-1])/self.train[-1]*100
        actual_revenue=(self.test[0]-self.train[-1])/self.train[-1]*100
        print("Today's value=%.2f ----Prediction=%.2f ----Actual value=%.2f ----Predicted revenue=%.2f" % (self.train[-1],last_value,self.test[0],predicted_revenue))
        if predicted_revenue>=0.8:
            print("-----Bought a "+str(indeces[self.id]) +" stock")
            self.my_money=self.my_money-100
            self.my_money=self.my_money+(100+1*actual_revenue)
            self.my_transaction_number +=1
            if actual_revenue>0:
                print("\033[0;37;42m You gained\033[0;37;42m "+str(round(1*actual_revenue,2))+"TL from this stock")
            else:
                print("\033[0;37;41m You losed\033[0;37;41m "+str(round(1*actual_revenue,2))+"TL from this stock")
            print(Style.RESET_ALL)
            
            
    def calculate_rmse(self):
        self.rmse=np.sqrt(sum(np.square(self.errors))/prediction_days)
        
        
        
        
indeces=["AFYON.IS","AKBNK.IS"]

total_days=len(yf.download(indeces[0], start="2019-01-02", end="2020-07-02"))
stock_objects=[]

for ids in range(n_of_stocks):
    stock_objects.append(Stocks(ids,indeces[ids]))

for days in range(prediction_days-1):
    print("-----------------------------THE %.i'ND DAY-------------------------------------" % days)
    print("--------TOTAL REVENUE=%.2f UNTIL %.i'ND DAY------------" % (total_revenue_until_today(),days))
    for my_stocks in range(n_of_stocks):
        #stock_objects[my_stocks].arimamodel()
        stock_objects[my_stocks].make_decision()
        stock_objects[my_stocks].update_train_and_test()
    
    #print("---------------TODAY YOU LOSED/GAINED -------------------------------------------" % sss)

    stock_objects[my_stocks].calculate_rmse()
